00:49:49,760 --> 00:49:51,250
有一天，他们会有梦想
one day, they'll have dreams.

588
00:49:51,460 --> 00:49:52,930
有一天，他们会有秘密
one day, they'll have secrets.

589
00:49:53,960 --> 00:49:55,950
有一天，他们会有梦想
one day, they'll have dreams.

590
00:50:04,770 --> 00:50:06,940
授权进入
Authorized entry.

591
00:50:11,580 --> 00:50:13,240
NS5
NS-5.

592
00:50:21,820 --> 00:50:23,190
桑尼？
Sonny?

593
00:50:27,200 --> 00:50:28,990
你怎么不回答？
Why didn't you respond?

594
00:50:30,930 --> 00:50:32,330
我在做梦
I was dreaming.

595
00:50:36,570 --> 00:50:38,730
很高兴再次见到你，凯文博士
I ' m glad to see you again, Dr. Calvin.

596
00:50:45,580 --> 00:50:48,070
他们会杀了我，是吗？
They are going to kill me, aren't they?

597
00:50:48,350 --> 00:50:51,790
在这个诊断之后，你会被销毁
You're scheduled to be decommissioned at the end of this diagnostic.

598
00:50:52,860 --> 00:50:54,720
明天晚上十点
2200 tomorrow.

599
00:50:55,860 --> 00:50:58,020
维基，暂停诊断
V.I.K.I., pause diagnostics.

600
00:50:58,230 --> 00:50:59,850
确认命令
Command confirmed.

601
00:51:02,230 --> 00:51:05,720
如果你找到我的问题所在 你能修好吗？
If you find out what is wrong with me, can you fix me?

602
00:51:07,170 --> 00:51:08,500
也许能
Maybe.

603
00:51:10,210 --> 00:51:12,440
我想如果能不死。。。
I think it would be better...

604
00:51:13,240 --> 00:51:14,500
会比较好
...not to die.

605
00:51:18,280 --> 00:51:19,940
是吗，博士？
Don't you, doctor?

606
00:51:25,620 --> 00:51:28,280
进入USR档案库
Access USR mainframe.

607
00:51:28,790 --> 00:51:30,120
连接中。。。
Connecting.

608
00:51:34,060 --> 00:51:36,400
我能为您服务吗？ 斯普那探员？
How can I be of service, Detective Spooner?

609
00:51:36,570 --> 00:51:40,060
给我兰尼博士和罗伯森之间的最后 50条信息
Show me the last 50 messages between Dr. Lanning and Robertson.

610
00:51:40,400 --> 00:51:44,740
语音识别确认，警用查询 允许查询限制档案
Voiceprint confirmed. Police access granted to restricted files.

611
00:51:44,910 --> 00:51:47,340
您等待时想听一些音乐吗？
Would you like to listen to music while you wait?

612
00:51:54,420 --> 00:51:56,580
对不起，罗伯森先生
Excuse me, Mr. Robertson.

613
00:51:56,920 --> 00:52:00,790
您要求在有查询限制档案时 向您报告
You requested notification of clearance to restricted files.

614
00:52:10,930 --> 00:52:13,090
真是顽固的杂种
Persistent son of a bitch.

615
00:52:53,340 --> 00:52:56,140
手动驾驶确认
Manual override engaged.

616
00:53:05,550 --> 00:53:07,850
我运气不会这么差吧？
There's no way my luck is that bad.

617
00:53:09,860 --> 00:53:11,490
哦，不！
Oh, hell, no!

618
00:53:15,460 --> 00:53:18,630
-您出了车祸！ -废话！
-You are experiencing a car accident. -The hell I am!

619
00:53:32,780 --> 00:53:34,370
滚开！
Get off my car!

620
00:53:50,530 --> 00:53:52,330
你喜欢这样？
You like that?

621
00:54:04,680 --> 00:54:06,410
你让我发火了！
Now you've pissed me off!

622
00:55:35,190 --> 00:55:37,810
您的门是打开的
Your door is ajar.

623
00:56:25,940 --> 00:56:27,370
好吧
Okay.

624
00:56:27,540 --> 00:56:29,370
算了
All right.

625
00:56:30,010 --> 00:56:33,210
休息一下，明天再处理这些事
I'll just get some rest and deal with you all tomorrow.

626
00:57:30,900 --> 00:57:33,060
来啊
Come on!

627
00:57:46,250 --> 00:57:47,650
是啊
Yeah.

628
00:58:05,140 --> 00:58:06,830
你去哪儿？
Where you going?

629
00:58:07,010 --> 00:58:09,100
你到底要怎么样？
What the hell do you want from me?!

630
00:58:15,210 --> 00:58:16,940
怎么搞的？
The hell was that?

631
00:58:33,730 --> 00:58:36,390
-情况怎么样？ -问问他
-All right, what do we got? -Ask him.

632
00:58:36,870 --> 00:58:41,360
我说了我没事 我会去看自己的医生，你退后吧
I said, I'm fine. I'll see my own doctor. Back up!

633
00:58:42,770 --> 00:58:44,370
谢谢你
Thank you.

634
00:58:47,650 --> 00:58:49,010
你怎么时候
What's the matter with you?

635
00:58:49,380 --> 00:58:54,010
交通部说你在手动开车 把两辆大卡车挤出了公路
Traffic Ops said you were driving manually. You ran two trucks off the road!

636
00:58:54,190 --> 00:58:56,920
约翰，机器人攻击我的车
John, the robots attacked my car.

637
00:58:58,660 --> 00:59:00,560
-什么机器人？ -看看隧道里面吧
-What robots? -Look in the tunnel.

638
00:59:00,730 --> 00:59:03,820
斯普，我刚刚就是从隧道过来的 什么机器人？
Spoon, I just came from that tunnel. What robots?

639
00:59:04,030 --> 00:59:06,390
就是他妈的机器人，约翰！
The goddamn robots, John!

640
00:59:10,900 --> 00:59:12,530
那个家伙不正常
That guy's a loose cannon.

641
00:59:17,410 --> 00:59:20,710
-去看医生，回家去 -不，我很好
-See the medic, go home. -No, I'm fine.

642
00:59:20,880 --> 00:59:22,540
你说什么？
What did you say?

643
00:59:22,710 --> 00:59:24,710
-我很好 -不，你才不是
-I'm fine! -No, you're not fine.

644
00:59:25,220 --> 00:59:26,910
一点都不好
Not even close.

645
00:59:28,320 --> 00:59:30,050
你的枪呢？
Where's your firearm?

646
00:59:38,300 --> 00:59:39,630
把警徽给我
Give me your badge.

647
00:59:40,930 --> 00:59:43,370
这是你自找的 把警徽给我
You're making me do this. Give me your badge.

648
00:59:46,240 --> 00:59:48,030
去休息。。。
Just take a couple--

649
00:59:52,580 --> 00:59:54,340
我个人认为他失掉这个警徽了
Personally, I think he's losing it.

650
00:59:54,510 --> 00:59:59,450
你觉得我很在乎吗？你觉得我在乎你怎么想的吗？
Do I look like I care what you think? Do I look like I give a shit what you think?

651
