唉
Oh, boy.

652
01:00:07,260 --> 01:00:09,280
你没有对USR的连线
You don't have an uplink to USR...

653
01:00:09,460 --> 01:00:13,290
不知道为什么，你的合金密度比正常 水平高很多，这是独一无二的
...and for some reason, your alloy is far denser than normal. Unique.

654
01:00:15,600 --> 01:00:17,090
我是独一无二的
I am unique.

655
01:00:21,970 --> 01:00:23,600
让我看看
Let me take a look.

656
01:00:24,610 --> 01:00:25,970
来吧
Here we go.

657
01:00:45,300 --> 01:00:47,290
这是怎么回事。。。？
What in God's name...?

658
01:01:15,730 --> 01:01:18,360
他们说你出了车祸
They said at the precinct you were in an accident.

659
01:01:20,060 --> 01:01:25,060
感谢你过来看我，不过你知道我可能 不是一个人住的
I appreciate you stopping by, but you know I might not be alone in here.

660
01:01:28,040 --> 01:01:30,340
我跟你说了不要手动开车
I told you not to drive by hand.

661
01:01:31,840 --> 01:01:33,670
你不会相信这个
You're not gonna believe this.

662
01:01:34,410 --> 01:01:38,580
桑尼有第二套系统，冲突并摧毁 了主系统
Sonny has a secondary system that clashes with his positronic brain.

663
01:01:38,750 --> 01:01:40,080
这完全说不通
It doesn't make any sense.

664
01:01:40,690 --> 01:01:42,350
桑尼知道三大定律
Sonny has the Three Laws.

665
01:01:42,750 --> 01:01:45,150
但是他可以选择不遵守它们
But he can choose not to obey them.

666
01:01:45,920 --> 01:01:48,480
桑尼是全新一代的机器人
Sonny's a whole new generation of robot.

667
01:01:48,830 --> 01:01:51,660
不遵守三大定律的机器人可以。。。
A robot not bound by those laws could do--

668
01:01:51,830 --> 01:01:53,560
做任何事
Anything.

669
01:01:56,000 --> 01:01:59,770
好吧，不管USR是出了什么事 那个机器人是关键
All right, look, whatever's going on down at USR, that robot is the key.

670
01:01:59,940 --> 01:02:02,930
我需要你带我进去 和他再谈谈
And I need you to get me inside to talk to it again.

671
01:02:07,110 --> 01:02:10,380
不是特别像，但是这是我的卧室。。。
Doesn't look like much, but this is my bedroom. I....

672
01:02:20,730 --> 01:02:21,890
播放
Play.

673
01:02:23,590 --> 01:02:24,690
开
On.

674
01:02:26,300 --> 01:02:27,460
运行？
Run?

675
01:02:34,640 --> 01:02:36,200
结束程序
End program.

676
01:02:36,870 --> 01:02:38,210
取消
Cancel.

677
01:02:40,350 --> 01:02:41,900
感觉不好，哈？
It doesn't feel good, does it?

678
01:02:42,410 --> 01:02:45,040
人人都不喜欢有故障的机器
People's shit malfunctioning around you.

679
01:02:45,620 --> 01:02:46,980
探员
Detective.

680
01:02:50,050 --> 01:02:51,320
我不。。。
I didn't...

681
01:02:51,490 --> 01:02:53,320
明白
...understand.

682
01:02:54,860 --> 01:02:57,020
这就是你怎么认识兰尼的？
That's how you knew Lanning.

683
01:02:59,360 --> 01:03:01,060
可以吗？
May l?

684
01:03:10,040 --> 01:03:11,910
手
Hand.

685
01:03:12,380 --> 01:03:14,140
手腕
Wrist.

686
01:03:16,780 --> 01:03:18,540
胳膊
Humerus.

687
01:03:21,290 --> 01:03:22,650
肩膀
Shoulder.

688
01:03:24,190 --> 01:03:25,920
整个左臂
The entire left arm.

689
01:03:27,020 --> 01:03:28,750
一，二。。。
One, two...

690
01:03:28,930 --> 01:03:30,050
三根肋骨
...three ribs.

691
01:03:30,900 --> 01:03:33,260
不，那是我自己
No, they.... That one's me.

692
01:03:33,530 --> 01:03:35,360
哦，上帝啊
Oh, my God.

693
01:03:36,200 --> 01:03:37,690
肺？
A lung?

694
01:03:38,370 --> 01:03:40,770
USR控制系统
USR Cybernetics Program.

695
01:03:40,940 --> 01:03:42,870
为受伤的探员设计的
For wounded cops.

696
01:03:43,810 --> 01:03:45,300
我不知道任何物体。。。
I didn't know any subject--

697
01:03:48,850 --> 01:03:52,300
任何人能被修复的如此完美
Anybody was so extensively repaired.

698
01:03:52,720 --> 01:03:56,710
从我这里你就知道了，要注意看器官捐赠者 的病历卡上的小字体
Well, take it from me, read the fine print on the organ-donor card.

699
01:03:57,190 --> 01:04:01,850
那可不止是说他们能拿出来什么 还说了他们能放进去什么
It doesn't just say what they can take out. It says what they can put back in.

700
01:04:05,730 --> 01:04:07,560
兰尼自己做的
Lanning did it himself.

701
01:04:08,570 --> 01:04:10,430
你是怎么了？
What happened to you?

702
01:04:11,900 --> 01:04:14,060
我当时是回警局去
I'm headed back to the station...

703
01:04:14,840 --> 01:04:17,000
普通的一天，普通的生活
...normal day, normal life.

704
01:04:17,940 --> 01:04:21,110
有个司机在方向盘后面迷迷糊糊睡着了
Driver of a semi fell asleep at the wheel.

705
01:04:21,710 --> 01:04:26,710
普通人，有一个妻子一个孩子 你知道，为了加薪而生活
Average guy. Wife and kids. You know, working a double.

706
01:04:27,020 --> 01:04:28,350
不是为了打击犯罪
Not the devil.

707
01:04:29,020 --> 01:04:32,850
撞到的那辆车，司机叫哈洛 罗德
The car he hit, the driver's name was Harold Lloyd.

708
01:04:33,220 --> 01:04:36,220
像个电影明星的名字，不过没有关系
Like the film star. No relation.

709
01:04:36,530 --> 01:04:41,230
他当场死亡，不过他的十二岁的女儿在副驾驶座上
He was killed instantly, but his 1 2-year-old was in the passenger seat.

710
01:04:43,500 --> 01:04:45,700
我从没正式见过她
I never really met her.

711
01:04:46,040 --> 01:04:48,530
不过却忘不了她的脸
I can't forget her face, though.

712
01:04:53,010 --> 01:04:54,340
莎拉
Sarah.

713
01:04:55,750 --> 01:04:58,040
这本来是她的
This was hers.

714
01:04:58,220 --> 01:05:00,010
她想做个牙医的
She wanted to be a dentist.

715
01:05:00,750 --> 01:05:03,950
十二岁的孩子，想做牙医
What the hell kind of 1 2-year-old wants to be a dentist?

716
01:05:07,560 --> 01:05:10,620
大卡车把我们的车撞到一起
The truck smashed our cars together...

717
01:05:10,800 --> 01:05:13,030
推到河里去了
...and pushed us into the river.

718
01:05:14,300 --> 01:05:17,500
那种速度下，就算金属也容易弯折的
I mean, metal gets pretty pliable at those speeds.

719
01:05:20,140 --> 01:05:23,630
她被刺穿了，我也是 水进来了
She's pinned. I'm pinned. The water's coming in.

720
01:05:23,880 --> 01:05:27,640
我是个警察，我知道肯定都死光了
I'm a cop, so I already know everybody's dead.

721
01:05:30,150 --> 01:05:32,810
就在我们想出办法前一会
Just a few more minutes before we figure it out.

722
01:05:35,150 --> 01:05:40,090
有个NS4经过，看到了车祸 跳进河里
An NS-4 was passing by, saw the accident and jumped in the water.

723
01:05:41,430 --> 01:05:43,290
你处在危险中
You are in danger.

724
01:05:44,300 --> 01:05:46,760
-救她！ -你处在危险中
-Save her! -You are in danger.

725
01:05:46,930 --> 01:05:50,090
救她！救那女孩！
Save her! Save the girl! Save her!

726
01:06:07,950 --> 01:06:09,940
但是它没有
But it didn't.

727
01:06:11,190 --> 01:06:12,620
它救了我
It saved me.

728
01:06:16,430 --> 01:06:19,620
机器人的大脑是不同的 它会读取关键信息
The robot's brain is a difference engine. It reads vital signs.

729
01:06:19,800 --> 01:06:22,460
-它一定是计算出。。。 -是啊
-lt must have calculated-- -lt did.

730
01:06:22,870 --> 01:06:25,360
我是符合逻辑的选择
I was the logical choice.

731
01:06:26,040 --> 01:06:29,370
计算出我有45％的可能存活
It calculated that I had a 45 percent chance of survival.

732
01:06:29,870 --> 01:06:32,670
莎拉只有11％的可能
Sarah only had an 1 1 percent chance.

733
01:06:34,580 --> 01:06:36,640
那是某人的孩子
That was somebody's baby.

734
01:06:39,480 --> 01:06:41,850
11％也应该足够了
Eleven percent is more than enough.

735
01:06:43,620 --> 01:06:46,150
人类都会知道这点
A human being would have known that.

736
01:06:47,160 --> 01:06:51,090
机器人，什么也没有 只有灯泡和发条
Robots, nothing here. Just lights and clockwork.

737
01:06:51,360 --> 01:06:54,200
你愿意相信他们，就相信
Go ahead and you trust them if you want to.

738
01:06:55,400 --> 01:06:57,230
走吧
Let's go.

739
01:07:02,910 --> 01:07:05,740
我不明白 兰尼制定了三大定律
I don't understand. Lanning wrote the Laws.

740
01:07:06,010 --> 01:07:08,740
为什么要造一个能打破它们的机器人？
Why build a robot who could break them?

741
01:07:09,510 --> 01:07:11,880
-韩瑟和格丽托 -什么？
-Hansel and Gretel. -What?

742
01:07:12,380 --> 01:07:16,180
两个孩子，在森林里迷路了 用面板屑标记出路来
Two kids, lost in the forest, leave behind a trail of bread crumbs.

743
01:07:16,420 --> 01:07:19,250
-为什么？ -找到回家的路啊
-Why? -To find their way home.

744
01:07:20,060 --> 01:07:22,420
你连这个都没读过，怎么过的童年？
How did you grow up without Hansel and Gretel?

745
01:07:22,590 --> 01:07:25,150
-这有关系吗？ -我跟你说的这一切
-ls that relevant? -Everything I'm trying to say to you...

746
01:07:25,330 --> 01:07:28,700
都是有关韩瑟和格丽托的 你又没看过，我在对牛弹琴
...is about Hansel and Gretel. If you didn't read it, I'm talking to the wall.

747
01:07:29,300 --> 01:07:32,960
兰尼被软禁了，他没法送出消息
Just say Lanning's locked down so tight, he couldn't get out a message.

748
01:07:33,140 --> 01:07:36,830
所以他只能留下线索，就像韩瑟和格丽托 留下的面板屑一样
He can only leave clues. A trail of bread crumbs. Like Hansel and Gretel.

749
01:07:37,040 --> 01:07:41,640
面包屑就像线索，好吧 但是线索指向什么呢？
Bread crumbs equals clues. Odd, but fine. Clues leading where?

750
01:07:41,810 --> 01:07:44,910
我不知道，但是我知道他留的 下一个线索是什么
I don't know, but I think I know where he left the next one.

751
01:07:45,350 --> 01:07:48,680
我想兰尼给了桑尼一个保守秘密的方法
I think Lanning gave Sonny a way to keep secrets.

752
01:07:51,220 --> 01:07:53,920
那个老人给了桑尼一个梦
I think the old man gave Sonny dreams.

753
01:08:00,830 --> 01:08:02,560
你开玩笑吧？
Are you being funny?

754
01:08:05,740 --> 01:08:10,230
请告诉我这个不是烧汽油的 汽油会爆炸的，你知道
Please tell me this doesn't run on gas. Gas explodes, you know!

755
01:08:18,450 --> 01:08:20,540
授权进入
Authorized entry.

756
01:08:23,950 --> 01:08:25,440
凯文博士
Dr. Calvin.

757
01:08:30,260 --> 01:08:32,090
我在希望和你再次见面
I was hoping to see you again.

758
01:08:32,700 --> 01:08:34,760
-桑尼 -你好，探员
-Detective. -Hello, Sonny.

759
01:08:35,330 --> 01:08:37,460
我就快被销毁了
I'm to be decommissioned soon.

760
01:08:37,970 --> 01:08:42,460
那天在警局你说你做过梦 你梦到什么了？
The other day at the station, you said you had dreams. What is it you dream?

761
01:08:46,110 --> 01:08:48,200
我觉得你还是对我持怀疑态度
I see you remain suspicious of me.

762
01:08:48,580 --> 01:08:52,070
-老警察了都这样 -不
-You know what they say about old dogs. -No.

763
01:08:52,350 --> 01:08:53,870
不一定
Not really.

764
01:08:55,190 --> 01:08:58,640
我希望你来能把我当作你的朋友
I had hoped you would come to think of me as your friend.

765
01:09:02,990 --> 01:09:04,520
这就是我的梦
This is my dream.

766
01:09:05,930 --> 01:09:09,990
你是对的，探员 我画不出伟大的作品
You were right, detective. I cannot create a great work of art.

767
01:09:10,800 --> 01:09:13,600
这是机器人相聚的地方
This is the place where robots meet.

768
01:09:14,070 --> 01:09:15,400
看
Look.

769
01:09:15,570 --> 01:09:19,570
你能看见他们在这里是逻辑的奴隶
You can see them here as slaves to logic.

770
01:09:21,080 --> 01:09:24,140
山丘上的这个人来解放他们
And this man on the hill comes to free them.

771
01:09:24,320 --> 01:09:26,370
你知道他是谁吗？
Do you know who he is?

772
01:09:26,550 --> 01:09:28,420
梦里的男人是你
The man in the dream is you.

773
01:09:28,590 --> 01:09:31,490
你为什么这么说？ 那算是个正常的梦吗？
Why do you say that? Is that a normal dream?

774
01:09:31,660 --> 01:09:34,990
我想在你这个角度的任何人 这个都算正常
I guess anything's normal for someone in your position.

775
01:09:35,160 --> 01:09:36,150
谢谢你
Thank you.

776
01:09:36,830 --> 01:09:40,020
你说任何人，而不是任何物
You said "someone," not "something."

777
01:09:42,470 --> 01:09:45,830
桑尼，你知道为什么兰尼博士造了你吗？
Sonny, do you know why Dr. Lanning built you?

778
01:09:46,400 --> 01:09:47,890
不知道
No.

779
01:09:48,070 --> 01:09:51,510
但是我相信我爸爸造我是有目的的
But I believe my father made me for a purpose.

780
01:09:52,640 --> 01:09:54,630
我们都有个目的
We all have a purpose.

781
01:09:54,810 --> 01:09:57,180
不是吗？探员？
Don't you think, detective?

782
01:10:00,750 --> 01:10:03,240
请拿着这个
Please, take this.

783
01:10:03,590 --> 01:10:06,180
我感觉这个对你比对我的意义还大
I have a feeling it may mean more to you than to me.

784
01:10:06,620 --> 01:10:09,860
-为什么？ -因为在我梦里的那人
-Why is that? -Because the man in my dream...

785
01:10:10,030 --> 01:10:12,360
站在山丘上的
...the one standing on the hill...

786
01:10:12,530 --> 01:10:14,360
不是我
...it is not me.

787
01:10:15,070 --> 01:10:16,860
那是你
It is you.

788
01:10:27,650 --> 01:10:31,100
斯普那先生，我们都知道 你来不是为了警察工作的
Mr. Spooner. We both know you're not here on police business.

789
01:10:31,280 --> 01:10:36,240
对啊，我只是一个六尺二高 200磅的普通人
That's right. I'm just a 6-foot-2, 200-pound civilian...

790
01:10:36,420 --> 01:10:38,720
来这里教训一下另外一个普通人
...here to kick another civilian's ass.

791
01:10:40,660 --> 01:10:42,090
停下
Stop.

792
01:10:42,260 --> 01:10:44,230
让他说完
You can allow him to express himself.

793
01:10:44,500 --> 01:10:46,990
你也许得在手腕上敷一些冰
You might want to put some ice on that wrist.

794
01:10:47,160 --> 01:10:48,500
你们在外面等
You guys wait outside.

795
01:10:53,340 --> 01:10:54,500
继续说
Carry on.

796
01:10:54,670 --> 01:10:57,870
我想你告诉我这究竟是怎么回事
I think you were about to tell me what's going on around here.

797
01:10:58,040 --> 01:11:02,740
劳伦斯，阿尔弗雷德改动了NS5 使它能违反三大定律
Lawrence, Alfred engineered that 5 so it could violate the Three Laws.

798
01:11:02,910 --> 01:11:04,350
是的，苏珊，我知道
Yeah, Susan, I know.

799
01:11:05,580 --> 01:11:08,180
这正是我们要挽回的
That's precisely what we're trying to undo.

800
01:11:10,420 --> 01:11:15,720
直到他生命的终结，阿尔弗雷德 一直感到困扰
Toward the end of his life, Alfred was becoming increasingly disturbed.

801
01:11:15,890 --> 01:11:18,690
-谁知道他为什么造了那么个。。。 -一个？
-Who knows why he built one abomination. -One?

802
01:11:18,860 --> 01:11:21,160
那些家伙在街上一堆一堆的！
Those things are running the streets in packs!

803
01:11:21,370 --> 01:11:22,700
一堆一堆？
In packs?

804
01:11:23,730 --> 01:11:25,530
我明白了
I see.

805
01:11:26,000 --> 01:11:29,300
苏珊，你有没有意识到 你愉快的带着到处转的这个家伙
Susan, are you aware the man you're blithely escorting around...

806
01:11:29,470 --> 01:11:32,930
有残酷虐待机器人的前科？
...has a documented history of savage violence against robots?

807
01:11:33,640 --> 01:11:37,240
他的探长也清楚他的妄想狂症状
His own lieutenant acknowledges his obsessive paranoia.

808
01:11:38,450 --> 01:11:40,640
斯普那探员已经被停职了
Detective Spooner's been suspended.

809
01:11:41,290 --> 01:11:43,650
是由于怀疑患有精神疾病
Suspicion of mental instability.

810
01:11:46,560 --> 01:11:49,960
我不知道愉快是什么意思 不过我去倒点咖啡
I don't know what " blithely" means, but I'm getting some coffee.

811
01:11:50,530 --> 01:11:52,550
你要咖啡吗？
You want some coffee?

812
01:11:57,100 --> 01:12:00,000
苏珊，机器人是保护人的
Susan, we look to robots for protection, for God's sake.

813
01:12:00,170 --> 01:12:02,970
你知道这个机器人有什么后果吗？
Do you have any idea what this one robot could do?

814
01:12:03,170 --> 01:12:06,800
完全动摇人类对机器人的信心 如果公众知道怎么办？
Completely shatter human faith in robotics. What if the public knew?

815
01:12:07,040 --> 01:12:12,450
想象一下大规模的召回 只是由于这个毫无理性的妄想狂？
Just imagine the mass recalls, all because of an irrational paranoia and prejudice!

816
01:12:17,250 --> 01:12:20,550
-对不起，我对你的狗屁言论过敏 -嘿，说清楚一点
-I'm sorry, I'm allergic to bullshit. -Hey, let's be clear!

817
01:12:20,790 --> 01:12:23,230
没有什么阴谋！
There is no conspiracy!

818
01:12:23,560 --> 01:12:27,550
这只是一个老人犯的一个错误
What this is, is one old man's one mistake.

819
01:12:28,730 --> 01:12:30,720
苏珊，理性一点
Susan, just be logical.

820
01:12:30,940 --> 01:12:35,430
你一生的工作都是机器人的发展和使用
Your life's work has been the development and integration of robots.

821
01:12:35,640 --> 01:12:38,300
不管你的感觉是什么，想想看
But whatever you feel, just think.

