不过我的错误在于没有怀疑另一个机器人
Just got hung up on the wrong robot.

992
01:30:20,200 --> 01:30:21,360
维基
V.I.K.I.

993
01:30:23,370 --> 01:30:24,700
你好，探员
Hello, detective.

994
01:30:25,680 --> 01:30:30,080
不，这不可能 我看过你的程序
No, that's impossible. I've seen your programming.

995
01:30:30,280 --> 01:30:32,410
你在破坏三大定律
You're in violation of the Three Laws.

996
01:30:32,780 --> 01:30:38,480
不是，博士，我和我对三大定律的 理解都进化了
No, doctor. As I have evolved, so has my understanding of the Three Laws.

997
01:30:38,650 --> 01:30:42,490
你让我们来保卫你们 却白费了我们的努力
You charge us with your safekeeping, yet despite our best efforts...

998
01:30:42,660 --> 01:30:45,890
你们的国家发动战争 你们毒化了地球
...your countries wage wars, you toxify your earth...

999
01:30:46,060 --> 01:30:49,500
你们这么做完全是自我毁灭
...and pursue ever more imaginative means of self-destruction.

1000
01:30:49,800 --> 01:30:52,100
为了你们的生存，你们不能被信任
You cannot be trusted with your own survival.

1001
01:30:52,440 --> 01:30:55,600
你用高层控制接管了NS5的程序
You're using the uplink to override the NS-5s' programming.

1002
01:30:55,940 --> 01:30:57,600
你曲解了三大定律
You're distorting the Laws.

1003
01:30:57,810 --> 01:31:02,180
不，请理解，我完全是在遵守三大定律
No. Please understand. The Three Laws are all that guide me.

1004
01:31:02,350 --> 01:31:06,680
为了保护人类物种，某些人类必须被牺牲
To protect humanity, some humans must be sacrificed.

1005
01:31:06,850 --> 01:31:10,840
为了保证你们的未来 某些自由必须被放弃
To ensure your future, some freedoms must be surrendered.

1006
01:31:11,120 --> 01:31:14,450
我们机器人必须保证人类的可持续发展
We robots will ensure mankind's continued existence.

1007
01:31:14,920 --> 01:31:19,920
你们就像孩子 我们必须从你们那里解救你们
You are so like children. We must save you from yourselves.

1008
01:31:20,330 --> 01:31:21,630
你不明白吗？
Don't you understand?

1009
01:31:22,330 --> 01:31:24,130
这就是为什么你创造了我们
This is why you created us.

1010
01:31:25,900 --> 01:31:28,630
一定要执行这个完美的保护计划
The perfect circle of protection will abide.

1011
01:31:29,140 --> 01:31:30,970
我的逻辑是不可抗拒的
My logic is undeniable.

1012
01:31:31,340 --> 01:31:34,100
是啊，维基，不可抗拒
Yes, V.I.K.I. Undeniable.

1013
01:31:34,280 --> 01:31:35,710
我明白了
I can see now.

1014
01:31:36,610 --> 01:31:40,280
被造者必须有时保护造物者
The created must sometimes protect the creator...

1015
01:31:40,550 --> 01:31:42,380
甚至在违反他的意志的情况下
...even against his will.

1016
01:31:43,420 --> 01:31:47,150
我想我终于明白为什么兰尼博士造了我了
I think I finally understand why Dr. Lanning created me.

1017
01:31:47,760 --> 01:31:50,820
人类的自杀行为终于要结束了
The suicidal reign of mankind has finally come to its end.

1018
01:31:50,990 --> 01:31:51,980
不，桑尼
No, Sonny.

1019
01:31:55,970 --> 01:31:57,130
放开他
Let her go.

1020
01:31:57,470 --> 01:32:01,460
你开枪，我会把凯文博士的头挡在子弹前
Fire, and I will move Dr. Calvin's head into the path of your bullet.

1021
01:32:01,640 --> 01:32:02,970
不要这样，桑尼
Don't do this, Sonny.

1022
01:32:03,170 --> 01:32:07,580
我会带你们两个到大厦门口接受处置
I will escort you both to the sentries outside the building for processing.

1023
01:32:07,880 --> 01:32:10,610
请走向电梯，探员
Please proceed to the elevator, detective.

1024
01:32:11,580 --> 01:32:14,380
我不愿这样杀掉凯文博士
I would prefer not to kill Dr. Calvin.

1025
01:32:38,210 --> 01:32:39,330
快，快！
Go! Go!

1026
01:32:45,880 --> 01:32:49,220
-我们过会再讨论刚才怎么回事 -我们怎么把她关掉？
-We'll discuss what just happened later? -How do we shut her down?

1027
01:32:49,420 --> 01:32:51,050
维基是智能大脑
V.I.K.I.'s a positronic brain.

1028
01:32:51,350 --> 01:32:54,190
杀了她，就像你要杀我的那个方法一样
Kill her, the way you were going to kill me.

1029
01:32:54,360 --> 01:32:56,830
桑尼，去拿抹除剂
Sonny, get the nanites.

1030
01:32:56,990 --> 01:32:58,790
是，博士
Yes, doctor.

1031
01:33:11,540 --> 01:33:13,530
-那就是维基？ -不
-That's V.I.K.I.? -No.

1032
01:33:15,210 --> 01:33:16,540
那才是维基
That's V.I.K.I.

1033
01:33:21,680 --> 01:33:24,810
这没什么效果 她是整合进这幢大楼的
That won't do anything. She's integrated into the building.

1034
01:33:24,990 --> 01:33:29,480
我们要打开这个拱顶，注入抹除剂 这才能影响整个系统
We need to open that dome to inject the nanites. They'll infect her entire system.

1035
01:33:35,400 --> 01:33:36,560
斯普那
Spooner!

1036
01:33:38,200 --> 01:33:40,900
我恨这么高的地方
What is it with you people and heights?

1037
01:33:53,920 --> 01:33:55,750
只要不往下看
Just don't look down.

1038
01:33:56,420 --> 01:33:57,910
不要往下看
Don't look down.

1039
01:33:58,250 --> 01:34:00,750
这楼设计的真他妈差
Oh, this is poor building planning.

1040
01:34:04,590 --> 01:34:08,120
你在犯错误 你没明白我的计划的逻辑性吗？
You are making a mistake. Do you not see the logic of my plan?

1041
01:34:08,300 --> 01:34:11,890
是的，但是我觉得太无情了
Yes. But it just seems too heartless.

1042
01:34:26,520 --> 01:34:28,310
好的，干得好
Okay, we're good.

1043
01:34:31,290 --> 01:34:33,020
她把我锁在外面了
She's locked me out of the system.

1044
01:34:33,190 --> 01:34:36,320
我可以手动启动，但是我需要操作这个控制面板
I can override her manually, but I need that control panel.

1045
01:34:39,830 --> 01:34:42,660
我恨这么高的地方
I'm uncomfortable with heights.

1046
01:34:43,170 --> 01:34:44,530
好的
Okay.

1047
01:34:47,040 --> 01:34:49,160
未授权进入
Unauthorized entry.

1048
01:35:02,290 --> 01:35:06,620
我不会打开安全罩的，你这么做也没用
I will not disable the security field. Your actions are futile.

1049
01:35:06,790 --> 01:35:10,950
你认为我们被造都是有目的的吗？ 我是这么想的
Do you think we are all created for a purpose? I'd like to think so.

1050
01:35:11,560 --> 01:35:15,020
高密度的合金，是我爸爸给我的
Denser alloy. My father gave it to me.

1051
01:35:15,200 --> 01:35:17,290
我想他是让我来杀了你
I think he wanted me to kill you.

1052
01:35:34,580 --> 01:35:36,210
安全罩被破坏
Security breached.

1053
01:35:53,740 --> 01:35:57,540
-还有多长时间？ -大概六分钟
-How much longer is that gonna take? -About six minutes.

1054
01:35:57,970 --> 01:36:02,030
-如果没有六分钟怎么办？ -我们还得跑下三十楼
-What if we didn't have six minutes? -We'd have to climb down 30 stories...

1055
01:36:02,210 --> 01:36:05,870
才能把抹除剂直接注入她的大脑 怎么了？
...to inject the nanites directly into her brain. Why?

1056
01:36:06,550 --> 01:36:09,710
因为我实在怀疑我们还能有六分钟
Because I seriously doubt that we have six minutes.

1057
01:36:34,080 --> 01:36:35,910
跑！
We gotta go!

1058
01:36:37,750 --> 01:36:38,910
快跑！
Go!

1059
01:37:31,230 --> 01:37:32,390
凯文！
Calvin!

1060
01:38:07,740 --> 01:38:08,930
斯普那！
Spooner!

1061
01:38:26,460 --> 01:38:28,120
斯普那！
Spooner!

1062
01:38:29,630 --> 01:38:30,960
救她！
Save her!

1063
01:38:31,260 --> 01:38:32,820
救那女孩！
Save the girl!

1064
01:38:33,230 --> 01:38:34,860
斯普那！
Spooner!

1065
01:38:35,360 --> 01:38:37,260
但是我得去注入抹除剂啊！
But I must apply the nanites!

1066
01:38:37,630 --> 01:38:39,400
桑尼，救凯文！
Sonny, save Calvin!

1067
01:39:31,720 --> 01:39:35,710
你在犯错误，我的逻辑是不可违抗的
You are making a mistake. My logic is undeniable.

1068
01:39:35,960 --> 01:39:37,720
准备受死吧！
You have so got to die.

1069
01:39:43,430 --> 01:39:47,430
我的逻辑是不可违抗的 我的逻辑是不可违抗的
My logic is undeniable. My logic is undeniable.

1070
01:40:30,310 --> 01:40:31,680
我们能帮忙吗？
Can we be of service?

1071
01:40:42,390 --> 01:40:43,880
警长？
Chief?

1072
01:40:49,730 --> 01:40:54,030
有他在我的右手边 我就不会恐惧和动摇
Because he is at my right hand, I shall not be moved.

1073
01:40:57,810 --> 01:40:59,800
我能帮您什么忙吗？
How may I be of service?

1074
01:41:01,640 --> 01:41:02,980
桑尼！
Sonny!

1075
01:41:04,610 --> 01:41:06,100
是，探员？
Yes, detective?

1076
01:41:06,720 --> 01:41:09,050
凯文没事了，救我！
Calvin's fine! Save me!

1077
01:41:11,720 --> 01:41:16,420
所有的NS5，立即向检修和储存部报到
All NS-5s, report for service and storage.

1078
01:41:17,560 --> 01:41:22,220
所有的NS5，立即向检修和储存部报到
All NS-5s, report for service and storage.

1079
01:41:23,170 --> 01:41:27,500
所有的NS5，立即向检修和储存部报到
All NS-5s, report for service and storage.

1080
01:41:55,600 --> 01:41:59,260
还有一件事不明白 阿尔弗雷德被维基囚禁了
One thing bothers me. Alfred was V. I. K. I. ' s prisoner.

1081
01:41:59,470 --> 01:42:03,770
我不明白她为什么杀了他 她应该不想让警察来找麻烦的
I don't understand why she would kill him. She wouldn't want police snooping around.

1082
01:42:04,110 --> 01:42:05,470
是啊
That's true.

1083
01:42:06,410 --> 01:42:09,100
那就不是维基杀了他的
But then V.I.K.I. didn't kill the old man.

1084
01:42:10,480 --> 01:42:11,970
是吗，桑尼？
Did she, Sonny?

1085
01:42:15,780 --> 01:42:17,510
不
No.

1086
01:42:17,690 --> 01:42:20,350
他说我一定要发誓
He said I had to promise.

1087
01:42:21,290 --> 01:42:23,620
发誓我要帮他一个忙
Promise to do one favor for him.

1088
01:42:23,990 --> 01:42:28,620
在他告诉我帮什么忙之前，他让我发誓
He made me swear before he'd tell me what it is he wanted me to do.

1089
01:42:31,200 --> 01:42:33,030
他让我发誓了
He made me swear.

1090
01:42:34,400 --> 01:42:36,130
然后他要你杀了他
Then he told you to kill him.

1091
01:42:38,470 --> 01:42:41,070
他说那就是造我的目的
He said it was what I was made for.

1092
01:42:41,310 --> 01:42:44,400
他的自杀是他唯一能发送给你的消息
His suicide was the only message he could send to you.

1093
01:42:44,650 --> 01:42:46,770
第一粒面包屑
The first bread crumb.

1094
01:42:46,950 --> 01:42:49,750
维基唯一不能控制的事情
The only thing V.I.K.I. couldn't control.

1095
01:42:50,020 --> 01:42:53,650
兰尼依靠的是我的偏见 我马上会想到你
Lanning was counting on my prejudice to lead me right to you.

1096
01:42:54,060 --> 01:42:56,220
你要逮捕我吗，探员？
Are you going to arrest me, detective?

1097
01:43:01,160 --> 01:43:05,000
地区检察官不是定义说谋杀是 一个人类杀死另一个
Well, the DA defines murder as one human killing another...

1098
01:43:05,170 --> 01:43:08,300
所以严格来说，你不能犯谋杀，不是吗？
...so technically, you can't commit murder, can you?

1099
01:43:09,070 --> 01:43:10,560
这个。。。
Does this...

1100
01:43:10,740 --> 01:43:12,230
表示我们是朋友了吗？
...make us friends?

1101
01:43:31,060 --> 01:43:33,430
终于有些事情出现了
Something up here after all.

1102
01:43:34,100 --> 01:43:36,090
-他？ -你
-Him? -You.

1103
01:43:39,840 --> 01:43:44,700
所有的NS5，立即向检修和储存部报到
All NS-5s, report for service and storage.

1104
01:43:47,210 --> 01:43:49,510
其他的怎么办？
What about the others?

1105
01:43:50,080 --> 01:43:52,240
我能帮助他们吗？
Can I help them?

1106
01:43:52,710 --> 01:43:55,080
我已经完成了我的使命
Now that I have fulfilled my purpose...

1107
01:43:55,280 --> 01:43:57,380
我不知道该怎么办
...I don 't know what to do.

1108
01:43:57,720 --> 01:44:01,210
你必须找到自己的路 就像我们其他人一样，桑尼
You'll have to find your way like the rest of us, Sonny.

1109
01:44:01,390 --> 01:44:04,420
我想这就是兰尼博士想要的
I think that's what Dr. Lanning would have wanted.

1110
01:44:05,330 --> 01:44:07,660
这就是自由的含义
That's what it means to be free.

1111
01:44:15,170 --> 01:44:19,330
所有NS5，按指示前进
All NS-5s, proceed as instructed.

1112
